==English==
===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|[punt]}}

===Noun===
#a narrow shallow boat propelled by a pole.
#(sport) In soccer, rugby, American football etc. a play where the ball is kicked upfield, usually without an intended receiver, in order to gain territory.
#a bet or wager.
#(metaphorical) a highly speculative investment or other commitment, a wild guess.
#(slang) a visit to a prostitute.

